title: MSNBC Blatantly LIES About Julian Assange Case
itunes:title: MSNBC Blatantly LIES About Julian Assange Case
description:
Julian Assange moved one step closer to extradition to the United States to face trumped-up Espionage Act charges. Jimmy and Glenn Greenwald discuss the case and the savage indictment of the U.S. and U.K. media the Assange case represents as alleged "journalists" cheer on the erosion of the free press.

Also featuring Stef Zamorano and Mike MacRae! Phone calls from Bernie Sanders and Anthony Fauci!
